<h1 id="Finding_Accounts">Finding Accounts</h1>

<p>All of the accounts in the Chart of Accounts are displayed by default.</p>

<img src="../../assets/images/documentation/chart_of_accounts/chart_of_accounts.png">

<p>To look for a specific account, type the account name in the search box and click search.</p>

<img src="../../assets/images/documentation/chart_of_accounts/account_search_step_1.png">

<img src="../../assets/images/documentation/chart_of_accounts/account_search_step_2_highlighted.png">

<img src="../../assets/images/documentation/chart_of_accounts/search_completed.png">

<h1 id="Creating_An_Account">Creating An Account</h1>

<p>To create an account, click on the <i>Create New Account</i> button.</p>

<img src="../../assets/images/documentation/chart_of_accounts/create_new_account_step_1.png">

<p>This will take you to the account creation page.</p>

<img src="../../assets/images/documentation/chart_of_accounts/account_creation.png">

<p>Enter the relevant information in each of the fields.</p>

<img src="../../assets/images/documentation/chart_of_accounts/account_creation_fields_filled.png">

<p>Then click on <i>Create Account</i>.</p>

<img src="../../assets/images/documentation/chart_of_accounts/account_creation__create_button_highlighted.png">

<img src="../../assets/images/documentation/chart_of_accounts/account_created.png">

<p>If you change your mind and do not want to create an account, click on <i>Back to Chart of Accounts</i>.</p>

<img src="../../assets/images/documentation/chart_of_accounts/account_creation_back_button_highlighted.png">

<img src="../../assets/images/documentation/chart_of_accounts/chart_of_accounts.png">

<h1 id="Editing_An_Account">Editing An Account</h1>

<p>To edit an account, click on the <i>edit</i> button.</p>

<img src="../../assets/images/documentation/chart_of_accounts/chart_of_accounts_edit_highlighted.png">

<p>This will take you to the editing account page.</p>

<img src="../../assets/images/documentation/chart_of_accounts/editing_account.png">

<p>Edit the fields with the desired values, and click <i>Update Account</i> to save the changes and go back to the Chart of Accounts page, or click on <i>Back to Chart of Accounts</i> to discard the changes and go back to the Chart of Accounts page.</p>

<p>An account with a balance greater than zero <strong>cannot</strong> be deactivated.</p>

